snippet.title: Puzzle Bobble 3D: Vacation Odyssey | PlayStation Announcement Trailer (PSVR, PS4, PS5)
snippet.description:
www.PuzzleBobble3D.com

For the first time in Puzzle Bobble history, bubble puzzles take 3-dimensional form to create new brain-teasing challenges for fans new and old to the franchise.

Learn more: https://blog.playstation.com/2021/06/03/puzzle-bobble-3d-vacation-odyssey-enters-a-new-dimension-on-ps-vr-ps4-and-ps5/
